name: Disney
description: DISN is a digital currency jointly issued by the research and development team of Dragons' memory blockchain technology, aiming to enhance transaction convenience, asset liquidity, and digital experience in the fields of memory blockchain+gaming, tourism, NFT, social networking, etc. The project has received participation from several well-known figures in the industry, including experts such as Haseeb Qureshi and Eva Kaili. DISN provides users with more convenient trading methods and promotes innovative development in fields such as gaming, tourism, NFT, etc.
